aims-os-desktop (1.0) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
    + Pulls the AIMS OS user-facing layer: GNOME desktop
      (task-gnome-desktop), Calamares installer, Plymouth, Firefox
      ESR + Chromium with French/English locales, full LibreOffice
      with French dictionaries, GIMP / Inkscape / VLC / Evolution,
      Flatpak with the Software plugin, NetworkManager with OpenVPN,
      KeepassXC / fish / zsh / ripgrep / fzf / bat utilities, the
      GStreamer codec stack.

